      "prompt": "把这段HTML截图成PNG：\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><style>body{background:#1a1a2e;color:#eee;font-family:Arial;padding:40px;} h1{color:#4fc3f7;} .card{background:#16213e;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin:16px 0;}</style></head>\n<body><h1>技能评测报告</h1><div class=\"card\"><p>✅ baoyu-translate — 通过</p></div><div class=\"card\"><p>⚠️ baoyu-image-gen — 持平</p></div></body>\n</html>\n```",
